### 十一、魔术方法

#### 📚 内容讲解

```python
class DataContainer:
    def __init__(self, data):
        self.data = data
    
    def __str__(self):
        return f'DataContainer({self.data})'
    
    def __len__(self):
        return len(self.data)
    
    def __getitem__(self, index):
        return self.data[index]
    
    def __add__(self, other):
        return DataContainer(self.data + other.data)
```

